  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a Space Wizard Samurai fugitive on the run.<br>The evil galactic emperor has declared that all “Space Wizard Samurai” must be exterminated.<br>Your only weapon… a saber to deflect laser beams.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your mission: <strong>survive</strong>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/37c06d7b1a3a9d6c5d86926bab8ec0c0.apng?t=1741927316\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/37c06d7b1a3a9d6c5d86926bab8ec0c0.poster.avif?t=1741927316\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=200 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/048e93ea8ab56577f547f0ddbbfa2587.poster.avif?t=1741927316\" width=618 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/048e93ea8ab56577f547f0ddbbfa2587.webm?t=1741927316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/048e93ea8ab56577f547f0ddbbfa2587.mp4?t=1741927316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deflect your enemy’s laser attacks and use it against them. Offensively!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/889f767c18d7b45ff4d8f5cda6549a79.apng?t=1741927316\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/889f767c18d7b45ff4d8f5cda6549a79.poster.avif?t=1741927316\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=200 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/a6cb68929cb3450d55acce6f5e0fa7ea.poster.avif?t=1741927316\" width=618 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/a6cb68929cb3450d55acce6f5e0fa7ea.webm?t=1741927316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/a6cb68929cb3450d55acce6f5e0fa7ea.mp4?t=1741927316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn and master various disciplines to achieve synergy and enlightenment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/a2510c3b9f398b3afbe2de18457fb4bf.apng?t=1741927316\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/a2510c3b9f398b3afbe2de18457fb4bf.poster.avif?t=1741927316\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=172 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/f7f3723853f2068fa1532a89b2dee072.poster.avif?t=1741927316\" width=600 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/f7f3723853f2068fa1532a89b2dee072.webm?t=1741927316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even though you’re alone, the power of the ‘Magic Space Chi’ will always be on your side.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/9393cee8a2939d1b3eb2f99590f3e517.apng?t=1741927316\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/9393cee8a2939d1b3eb2f99590f3e517.poster.avif?t=1741927316\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=240 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/a57d154140677b28cb58586540102864.poster.avif?t=1741927316\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/a57d154140677b28cb58586540102864.webm?t=1741927316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/a57d154140677b28cb58586540102864.mp4?t=1741927316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The best art style of the 80s, when Space Wizard Samurai was cool.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/429fbe30e6bbab832fb2638ba390e0a4.apng?t=1741927316\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/429fbe30e6bbab832fb2638ba390e0a4.poster.avif?t=1741927316\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=200 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/a2ee78bba7822c8a7321938504571e62.poster.avif?t=1741927316\" width=618 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/a2ee78bba7822c8a7321938504571e62.webm?t=1741927316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/a2ee78bba7822c8a7321938504571e62.mp4?t=1741927316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quick play session for optimum burst of fun gameplay. Reach climax in no more than 15 minutes per session.</p>",
